snippet.textDisplay:
Yes, we have now entered a time when intelligent conversation thru genuine connection has lead towards the truth, partnership and unity that challenges the old tough investigative journalist interview formats. We're tired of being and seeing others attacked. It's extremely insulting even more presumptuous to think that we are more inclined to fall for the divisive drama and tension than we are for seeing genuine connection, brotherhood & sisterhood which leads to growth #thebag....it gets to heavy for one person to carry alone.
Sean,
Thank you for your persistence and consistency over the year. Your connectivity to the truth has lead to some of the most entertaining and creative conversations about content creation concept, after concept. Taking that risk to be great, while terrifically repping for the home team. The whole Midwest for real. For years you remain, so many years as a great. Your contribution will always be remembered 100's of years from now as a pioneer in the industry.... An industry which is now, still in it's infancy. Thank you Sean for your contribution. We can't wait to see what's yet to come.
